quran[37]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,Alcaaqha is Qhiyaamâ migaqwak migaaqak teynay is nummah takku waytam yascasse kinni
  69,2,Qhiyaamay cakkil takku wayta macaay
  69,3,Maca koo tiysixxigeeh Nabiyow Qhiyaamay cakkil takku wayta
  69,4,Samuud deqsitta kedoó (woh Nabii Saalic mara) kee Qaad deqsitta kedó (woh Nabii Huud mara) Qhiyaamay meesî gibdah lubbî taatuki deqsitta dirabbosseh
  69,5,"Tokkel samuuduh tu gactek, Yalli caddok taturte xongolot ken finqise"
  69,6,"Kaadu Qaad deqsita marah tu gactek, Yalli kaxxa xongoloo kee xabca le caacayay caddok tatret ken finqise"
  69,7,"Yalli malcina baraay bacra ayroy sitta katattay aggirriqqe sinni caacay keenit ruube, tokkel woo baritteé kee woo ayroorah addat sinaamay rabtey qangalaltay tamiirâ laqiibay gorrittey inaaqah tani ceelah ken table"
  69,8,Tokkel woo marak numwy finqite kalah raaqe keenik maay table
  69,9,"Kaadu firqawnaay, kaak naharat korosuh suge maraá kee magaalol elle korsen mari (Nabii Luut mara kinnuk) kaxxa dambi luk yemeeten"
  69,10,"Tokkel usun sinni Rabbih farmoyta cineenih, wonnaluk Yalli gibdi mabbuxuh ken yibbixe (digaalá kinnuk)"
  69,11,"Diggah nanu lee caddok taturteeh kulliimik amo ciggilte waqdi, doynikit Nabii Nuucùû luk sin nukkuqeeh sin raaqisne"
  69,12,"Woo abto kassis siinih abne, kaadu raaqissa ayti tet raaqissamkeh"
  69,13,Tokkel baantat inki adda fuuxa fuuxumta waqdi
  69,14,"Kaadu baaxoo kee qaleelá le aroocak tamukkuqeeh, inki atkah sittat tamuttukeeh bulá takke"
  69,15,Toysa too waqdi Qhiyaama soltah
  69,16,"Kaadu qaran qanxixaah, usuk woo ayró boolaataah Qande luk maraaqa"
  69,17,"Kaadu malayka kay deraafel gactaah, woo ayró ku Rabbih qarshi malaykak bacra malaykatti isi amol yakkuqe"
  69,18,"Too ayró sinaamey cisab kee galtoh Yallî fooca sin maksan, isin qellissaanamak tu kaak maqellitta"
  69,19,Le kitab migdi gabah kah yontocowwime numuh tugactek wallê gibdah yi kitab ibbixa ikriya iyya
  69,20,"Diggah anu asmatuk suge, inni cisaabat (galtot) garayuwaam"
  69,21,Toysa usuk akeeral ruffu kaa hayta mano le
  69,22,Jannatay fayya leh addal yan
  69,23,Jannatti mexexi kaa daggaasita marah xayih
  69,24,"Keenik iyyaanah:akumaay, aquba ruffû xica tatrusutten meqe taamáh sabbatah, taturte ayroorah addat"
  69,25,"Kaadu Le kitab guri gabah kah yontocowwime numuh tu gactek, maganey yi kitab yoh antacawwime wannay iyya"
  69,26,Kaadu inkinnah maa xaginniyo yicisab kinnim
  69,27,Maganey addunyal abe rabi yi manoh ellecabo akkinnay
  69,28,Yi maali yoh xiqem mali Yallih digaalák
  69,29,Yi duddaa kee reedá yok gexxeh
  69,30,"Iyyan jahannam malaykak:kaa abbixaay wonnaluk kay namma gaba fillat kaak axuwa silsilatat"
  69,31,Tohuk lakal jaciim deqsitta girá kaa culusa tet niqna tammoysamkeh
  69,32,Tohuk lakal silsilatay xexxaarah malcina tabanih cusul yakket kaa culusa iyyan
  69,33,Diggah usuk addunyal Yallay nabah inkittinaanel aamanuk masuginna
  69,34,Kaadu tu dagoyta yaskameenimih sinam ilsiisak masuginna addunyal
  69,35,Toysa ta saaku usuk takkķel isil xayi numuy digaalá isik waasa mali
  69,36,Kaadu hebeltô maaqo mali girâ marak caxta qasaalayi akke waytek
  69,37,Ama qasaalayi takmem matan dambileelay koroosannuk kate wayte akke waytek